query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('asp.net-core',
'asp.net-mvc-4',
'c',
'ionic-framework',
'linux',
'ms-word',
'namespaces',
'node.js',
'null',
'process',
'scikit-learn',
'shiny',
'sockets',
'validation',
'x86');
